<title>USA: Excel extends share buyback plan.</title>
<headline>Excel extends share buyback plan.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1997-05-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Excel Communications Inc said it was extending its share repurchasing program until further notice.</p>
<p>Under the program, which was announced May 1 and was to have been in effect until May 23, Excel plans to buy back up to two million shares.</p>
<p>Excel is a long-distance company.</p>
<p>((-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610))</p>
